MNIST task by Yann Lecun
------------------------
Handwritten digits (10 classes) as 256-level gray-scale images of 28 x 28 pixels. 
Training set includes 60K images and test set, 10K images.
Samples are organised by rows both, image and label files.
Corpus web: http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/

Variable  Set  Type   File  
--------  ---- ------ ----
X         tr   images train-images-idx3-ubyte.mat.gz
xl        tr   labels train-labels-idx1-ubyte.mat.gz
Y         test images t10k-images-idx3-ubyte.mat.gz
yl        test labels t10k-labels-idx1-ubyte.mat.gz

Execute bash script 00-preprocess.sh to download and preprocess MNIST.
